data.description: Welcome home this luxurious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhome provides plenty of space for a modern lifestyle-It features an open concept living and dining area with tons of natural light-a cozy kitchen with stainless steel appliances with reverse osmosis which is also connected to the refrigerator-a master suite with an en suite bathroom and walk-in closet-two additional bedrooms have plenty of space for family or guests-with a bonus room between the 2 bedrooms which makes a great play area or media room-The townhome also boast tile floors on main level and carpet on 2nd floor-a large two-car garage-a private backyard patio perfect for entertaining-no back neighbors-This is the perfect home for any family looking for the perfect combination of style and comfort located in the award winning Meridiana Subdivision-Amenities include lazy river with wave pool-2 gyms-family & kiddie pool-tennis, basketball, volleyball courts-numerous play grounds-lakes you can fish in-pickle ball court
